com.ab.listeners

Class ListenersClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ab.listeners.ListenersClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.testng.ISuiteListener, org.testng.ITestListener, org.testng.ITestNGListener

    public class ListenersClass
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.testng.ITestListener, org.testng.ISuiteListener

    The ListenersClass class implements ITestListener and ISuiteListener to listen to events in a test automation framework. It creates, adds authors and suites to tests, and logs results to the Extent report.
